      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep waking up and for a split second i forget, and then the silence hits me all over again. it’s like the house is just an empty shell. i don't even know why i bother getting out of bed or making coffee anymore. what's the point of just going through the motions when the only person who made it feel real is gone?",
