    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i’m living in a world where i don't belong anymore. like i'm just a shadow walking through rooms that don't belong to me. i look at my life and there's nothing left. no future, no purpose... just this endless, heavy nothingness. i'm so tired of pretending that things will eventually get better. what if they don't? what if this is just how it is now?",
