    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting... the constant dragging of myself through every day. honestly, sometimes i look at the empty side of the bed and i just think how much easier it would be if the silence was permanent. if i didn't have to wake up to this emptiness every single morning. does it make sense that i just want to stop existing?",
